metadata.name: tomorrow
metadata.description:
"hark a spark of madness in my mind  
flickering in the dark, a candle alight  
burning through the night, it consumes my soul  
reducing me to naught but a cackling shell

i am lost to madness, consumed by fire  
flames of insanity lick at my sanity  
till all that remains is this burning pyre  
of my once sound mind, now a charred memory"
